WAP to check if a given string is palindrome or not.

A string is called palindrome if the reverse of the string is the same as 
the original one.

input : racecar
        racecar
        
        madam
        madam
        
        malayalam
        malayalam
        
WAP to find out all the available Palindrome words present in a given string.        

length, charAt, equals, toLowerCase, toUpperCase, replace, substring, concat

